chapter_id = "chapter_02"
label = "Unseen"
text = "You reach the dig site an hour ahead of anyone who might have stopped you, following a route Kestrel's crew never bothered to watch. The shaft opens into a chamber that isn't natural, and isn't Halcyon construction either. The air tastes faintly of frost, the way Kharon-9's corridors did."
